        <h1>Travel to Seattle</h1>
    
        <h2>Basic facts</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>The largest city in the Pacific Northwest.</li>
            <li>The home of <strong>Starbucks</strong>, <strong>Microsoft</strong>, and <strong><em>freaking Nirvana</em></strong>.</li>
            <li>Pretty cool.</li>
        </ul>
        <img src = "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/2f/Space_Needle002.jpg/280px-Space_Needle002.jpg" alt = "Seattle, Washington" width = "350">
        <h2>Top five Seattle attractions</h2>
        <ol>
            <li><h3>The Space Needle</h3>
                <img src = "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b6/Seattle_Space_Needle_Victor_Grigas.jpg/1024px-Seattle_Space_Needle_Victor_Grigas.jpg" alt = "the space needle" width = "250">
                <p>Pretty tall and stuff.</p>
            </li>
             <li><h3>The Pacific Science Center</h3>
                <img src = "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/ab/Pacific_Science_Center_at_night_02.jpg/640px-Pacific_Science_Center_at_night_02.jpg" alt = "the pacific science center" width = "250">
                <p>Great for kids to learn about science and centers.</p>
            </li>
            <li><h3>Pike Place Market</h3>
                <img src = "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/2/2a/PikePlaceMarket.jpg/640px-PikePlaceMarket.jpg" alt = "pike place market" width = "250">
                <p>They sell many things, but no pikes.</p>
            </li>
            <li><h3>Chihuly Garden and Glass</h3>
                <img src = "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/06/Glass.sculpture.kewgardens.london.arp.jpg/716px-Glass.sculpture.kewgardens.london.arp.jpg" alt = "chihuly garden and glass" width = "250">
                <p>These glass sculptures will blow your mind.</p>
            </li>
            <li><h3>The Museum of Pop Culture</h3>
                <img src = "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/09/EMPPano11.jpg/1280px-EMPPano11.jpg" alt = "the museum of pop culture" width = "250">
                <p>Oh, man, this is so cool -- they've got Daleks and a guitar tornado and a recoding studio and stuff.</p>
            </li>
        </ol>
        <h2 id="soundgarden">Soundgarden</h2>
        <p>The greatest band of the grunge era is also from Seattle. Below, you will find the lyrics to their most beautiful and awesome song. RIP CHRIS.</p>
        <h3>Like Suicide</h3>
        <p class="verse-a">Heard it from another room<br>
